name: Feed the Customers
description:
A little game about surviving as long as you can,  it's fun enough I guess. Anyways have a nice day.

Use the 1 2 and 3 keys to switch foods, mouse to aim, and click to throw.

The audio got messed up while packaging the game, so I might update it if I can figure out how to fix it.
